dc_title_s: Elevation Data, Steep & Severe Slopes: Prince George's County, Maryland, 2014
dc_description_s: This dataset show steep and severe slopes developed from a DEM dataset for Prince George's County. This includes slopes with a percent rise between 15% and 25%, and greater than 25%. This data was captured for use in general mapping at a scale of 1:1200.
dc_creator_sm: The Maryland-National Capital Park & Planning Commission
